A developer wishes to:

Automatically test package functions,
Publish package documentation as a website,
Expose selected functions through a REST API,
Run the API through an HTTP server.

Which sequence of packages is most appropriate?

A. testthat → pkgdown → plumber → httpuv

B. pkgdown → testthat → httpuv → plumber

C. plumber → httpuv → testthat → pkgdown

D. testthat → plumber → pkgdown → httpuv

Answer: A.
